      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cverse2",
        "text": "And he said, Unto you it is given to know the {a} mysteries of the kingdom of God: but to others in parables; that seeing they might not see, and hearing they might not understand.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "And he said, Unto you it is given to know the ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "cverse3",
            "text": "{a}",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " mysteries of the kingdom of God: but to others in parables; that seeing they might not see, and hearing they might not understand.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(a) Those things are called secret which may not be uttered: for the word used here is equivalent to our saying, to hold a man's peace.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
